# Copy to `.dev.vars` for local development. Do not commit `.dev.vars`.

# Keep the first-launch setup wizard hidden locally; its Cloudflare ownership
# verification cannot run on localhost. Local GitHub identity comes from
# http://localhost:5173/setup/local instead (see docs/development.md).
NANITES_SHOW_SETUP="false"

# GitHub App credentials (`GITHUB_APP_<ID>_PRIVATE_KEY`, `GITHUB_APP_<ID>_CLIENT_SECRET`,
# `GITHUB_APP_<ID>_WEBHOOK_SECRET`) and `AUTH_COOKIE_SECRET` are not typed in by hand:
# creating a dev GitHub App at /setup/local prints the exact block to append here.

# Required only when using ALLOW_TEST_AUTH=true for local MCP/browser smoke tests.
GITHUB_TEST_USER_TOKEN=""

# Optional Sentry runtime secret.
SENTRY_DSN=""
